These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, house, salsa, reggae
1. the fan of house is between the fan of salsa and the fan of reggae##2
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of country is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | country | reggae | house | salsa |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, water, milk, 7up
1. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person drinking 7up is between the person drinking water and the person drinking juice##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | water | 7up | juice | milk |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different pets are kept: goat, frog, horse, guinea-pig
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the horse is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
3. the owner of the goat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | goat | guinea-pig | horse | frog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, cucumber, apricot, spinach
1. the person eating apricot is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating pumpkin##2
2. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
3. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food   | spinach | cucumber | apricot | pumpkin |

